snippet.title: Mortal Kombat 1 – Official Omni-Man First Look
snippet.description:
The realms will tremble under the weight of the Viltrum Empire. Omni-Man approaches our timeline.

Get the Premium Edition now to play as Omni-Man: https://www.mortalkombat.com/purchase

It's In Our Blood. Discover a reborn Mortal Kombat Universe created by Fire God Liu Kang. Mortal Kombat 1 ushers in a new era of the iconic franchise with a new fighting system, game modes, and Fatalities!
